<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>로그인 - GS Retail</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<!-- fullpop :: 약관 동의 -->
	<div id="pop01" class="fullPop">
		<h1>약관 동의</h1>
		<div class="popCon">
			<div class="termsArea line">
				<div class="titArea">
					<h2 class="titDep1">GS리테일 서비스 이용약관 동의</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="totalCheck">
					<span class="checkForm">
						<input type="checkbox" id="totalAgree">
						<label for="totalAgree">전체 동의</label>
					</span>
					<a href="#" style="display:block;">전체동의 약관 보기</a>
					<button type="button" aria-expanded="false" style="display:none;">약관목록보기</button>
				</div>
				<ul class="acc" style="display:block;">
					<li>
						<div class="accTit necessary">
							<span class="checkForm">
								<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck01">
								<label for="termsCheck01">[필수]GS리테일 회원약관 동의</label>
							</span>
							<button type="button" aria-expanded="false" title="약관 목록 보기"><b class="point">[필수]</b> GS리테일 회원약관 동의</button>
						</div>
						<div class="accCon">
							<ul class="subTerms">
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">GS리테일 멤버십(THE POP) 회원약관</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">GS리테일 서비스 앱 이용약관</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">GS fresh 웹 회원약관</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li>
						<div class="accTit necessary">
							<span class="checkForm">
								<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck02">
								<label for="termsCheck02">[필수]GS리테일 개인정보 보호를 위한 이용약관 동의</label>
							</span>
							<button type="button" aria-expanded="false" title="약관 목록 보기"><b class="point">[필수]</b> GS리테일 개인정보 보호를 위한 이용약관 동의</button>
						</div>
						<div class="accCon">
							<ul class="subTerms">
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">수집하는 개인정보 항목 및 이용목적</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">보유기간 및 파기</a></li>
								<li><a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기">개인정보 처리위탁 동의</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</li>
					<li class="along">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck03">
							<label for="termsCheck03">[선택]GS리테일 개인정보 제3자 제공 동의</label>
						</span>
						<a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기"><b>[선택]</b> GS리테일 개인정보 제3자 제공 동의</a>
					</li>
					<li class="along">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck04">
							<label for="termsCheck04">[선택]위치기반 서비스 이용약관 동의</label>
						</span>
						<a href="#" role="button" title="약관보기"><b>[선택]</b> 위치기반 서비스 이용약관 동의</a>
					</li>
					<li class="along onLyCheck">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck05">
							<label for="termsCheck05">[선택]PUSH 알림 수신 동의</label>
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="along onLyCheck">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck06">
							<label for="termsCheck06">[선택]문자(SMS) 정보 수신 동의</label>
						</span>
					</li>
					<li class="along onLyCheck">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="checkbox" id="termsCheck07">
							<label for="termsCheck07">[선택]이메일 정보 수신 동의</label>
						</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<div class="btnArea">
					<button type="button" class="btnTS btnL active">확인</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<button type="button" class="btnClose">팝업 닫기</button>
	</div>
	<!-- //fullpop :: 약관 동의 -->
</body>
</html>

